checkGeneratorProviderFile

protected void checkGeneratorProviderFile(java.lang.String path)
Check if the supplied path point to a generator provider class. If it does so, analyse it. Should it be feasible, try to get a generator from it. While doing so add information to the text widgets.

Parameters:
path - The path to the generator provider.
